text: Future-Worm! is an American comic science fiction animated television series. It was created by Ryan Quincy, who previously created IFC's Out There, for Disney XD. The show features the adventures of Danny and Future-Worm, who time travel by using a lunch box-shaped time machine. The series aired from August 1, 2016 to May 19, 2018.
